  "detailed_description": "Peril is a retro action adventure 2d platformer. In this game the player must battle through various worlds and defeat many enemies, all the while using a javelin as both a weapon and a tool to reach new places.<br><br><strong>Battle against dangerous enemies</strong><br>-Over 40 different enemies to face<br>-7 unique and challenging bosses<br>-Choose to slice them with your sword or snipe them with your javelin<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/41709a213cf28a94cd131886c01a91dc.poster.avif?t=1692013087\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/41709a213cf28a94cd131886c01a91dc.webm?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/41709a213cf28a94cd131886c01a91dc.mp4?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/7ba18061c3973e4c68d02973db8850bd.webp?t=1692013087\" width=480 height=40 /></span><br><br><strong>Upgrade character stats</strong><br>-Collect gems and coins to upgrade your sword strength, javelin power, max health, or javelin capacity<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/e9d977deecc4926db3816bf926a6f01b.poster.avif?t=1692013087\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/e9d977deecc4926db3816bf926a6f01b.webm?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/e9d977deecc4926db3816bf926a6f01b.mp4?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Use your Javelin to jump across obstacles</strong><br>-Master the art of throwing your javelin to make a new platform<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/028438e0f4c7c14480c8177eb92d09bd.poster.avif?t=1692013087\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/028438e0f4c7c14480c8177eb92d09bd.webm?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/028438e0f4c7c14480c8177eb92d09bd.mp4?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/b7c6f64ea306e35a0effdd9fda7e7da2.webp?t=1692013087\" width=480 height=40 /></span><br><br><strong>Solve puzzles</strong><br>-Puzzles are built to be solves in many unique ways. The javelin can provide some creative solutions to challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/d998574e77024ade6ef7919cde7cf95d.poster.avif?t=1692013087\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/d998574e77024ade6ef7919cde7cf95d.webm?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/d998574e77024ade6ef7919cde7cf95d.mp4?t=1692013087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798910/extras/c0aac65b67faa4bfafcea9afa9e9c820.webp?t=1692013087\" width=480 height=40 /></span>",
